description: Pristine home located in the heart of South Boston. Enjoy a bright, open layout featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and large island. Two generous size bedrooms with oversized closets. Primary bedroom easily fits a king size bed with ensuite with built in window/storage seating. Secondary bedroom fits a queen size bed. Many recent upgrades include freshly painted, hardwood floors throughout have been finished, washer/dryer new in 2024, new dishwasher, refrigerator replaced in 2023, surround sound, iPod dock.  Central A/C, gas fireplace, storage, private deck. Located steps from restaurants, shops, minutes to the South Boston Seaport, immediate highway access.
